<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>هَذَا آخِرُ بَابٍ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مِنْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>كِتَابِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«التُّفَّاحَةِ فِي النَّحْوِ»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَبهِ تَمَّ الشَرْحُ المُسَمَّى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِينَاس النَّاسِ بتُفَّاحَةِ أَبي جَعْفَر النَّحَّاس»</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>واللهُ المُيَسِّرُ والمُعِينُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَأَسْألُهُ - سُبْحَانَهُ - أَنْ يُقِرَّ هَذَا الشَّرْحَ في مِيزَانِ الأَعْمَالِ الصَّالِحَاتِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَالحَمْدُ للهِ رَبِّ العَالَمِين<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>